  3.980892984361601*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1b1f9243-389e-0b4f-9100-\
17b6bfe6bb89"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook implements the data cleaning, outbreak detection, \
counterfactual scenario analyses, and bootstrap uncertainty quantification \
used in the manuscript . 
Outputs include : \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.980892995141474*^9, 3.9808930453135643`*^9}, {
  3.9808930777523613`*^9, 
